<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />从刚才开始，就有很多流星划过天边<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
心里想着是不是还会再有流星，<delay8 />
根本不敢移开视线呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我一直抬头望着天空，<delay8 />
想着能不能见到流星<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果脖子现在<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为流星的美丽所震慑，<delay20 />
我都忘记<delay8 />
要许愿的事情了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看见彩虹，就会让人感觉很幸福。<delay20 />
如果身边还有陪你一起看彩虹的人，<delay8 />
幸福就会变成两倍了，对不对？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">多漂亮的彩虹<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在它面前，感觉那些微不足道的烦恼<delay8 />
都烟消云散了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雨后的彩虹……<delay20 />
看起来就像是<delay8 />太阳赐予的祝福呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然能看见双重彩虹，<delay8 />
今天的运气可真好呀～<delay20 />
总感觉<delay8 />还会有其他好事发生！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />双重彩虹，<delay8 />这是何等地美妙<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />发生这种少见的事情，<delay20 />
会让我开始怀疑<delay8 /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 /><tag a="110" b="0" />这会不会是<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />某种大事件的前兆呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">天空中极为罕见地出现了两道彩虹，<delay20 />
随后它们开始缓缓消逝<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如此美景，一定要观赏到最后。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">在冬日夜空中闪耀的极光<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />面对这自然向我们展示的神秘景观，<delay20 />
根本无法别过眼去啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为光纱所笼罩的夜空<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />莫非在它的另一侧，<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />掩藏着什么<delay8 />
不想让我们知道的秘密吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />阴暗冰冷的寒空……<delay20 />
反倒更让这华丽而闪耀的极光<delay8 />
显得愈加美丽呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />留下那条飞机云的飞机……<delay20 />
究竟会飞向哪座<tag a="110" b="32" />呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">在蓝天下笔直延伸的飞机云<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让人有一种<delay8 />
非常清爽的感觉呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一看见飞机云，<delay20 />
突然就想来一场旅行了……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如此完美的圆<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
看到这满月的美景，<delay20 />
感觉自己的心灵也被填满了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">满月这种明亮柔和的光……<delay20 />
有着太阳那强烈的光所不具备的魅力哦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且还可以像这样一直注视着它。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />伴着满月的光亮，<delay8 />
会让夜晚的散步更加美妙哦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这可是每个月才有一次的<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />享受！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>